description.narrative: This activity (Civil Society Challenge Fund) is a component of Civil Society Challenge Fund reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Not for profit organisation' and a budget of £50,027,543. This component benefits Developing countries, unspecified, and works in the following sector(s): Democratic participation and civil society. , with the following implementing partners: IOD PARC, KPMG LLP, Triple Line. The start date is 15-01-2010 and the end date is 30-09-2015.
